subject: HISTORY
text: Give the century, B.C. or A.D., of each of the following, indicate who or what each was, and say why each is important in history: the Algeciras Conference, Roger Bacon, Hugh Capet, the Council of Constance, the Emperor Constantine, Copernicus, the Edict of Nantes, Louis Pasteur, the Battle of Salamis, the Peace of Westphalia.
